GET
/api/public/faqs/
Get FAQs


Returns active FAQs. Results are paginated (default 20/page).

Filter: ?category=fpo_general / schemes / platform_usage

Pagination: ?page=1&page_size=20 (max 100)

Send X-Language: ml to get Malayalam text where available.

Results are Redis-cached (24h). Cache is cleared automatically when an FAQ is created, updated, or deleted.

Parameters
Cancel
No parameters

Execute
Clear
Responses
Curl

curl -X 'GET' \
  'http://localhost:8000/api/public/faqs/' \
  -H 'accept: */*'
Request URL
http://localhost:8000/api/public/faqs/
